{"tid":1630701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個時世坐咩車都唔安全,你地同我買部單車","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:44:58.000Z","uid":137480,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2292b4d8f54e05efc5f493f6e160c9910c243d5f","tid":1630701,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"踏單車可以係1-2區之內機動遊走<br />\n<br />\n單車細部可以入巷仔,走佬是狗車追唔到狗又跑得唔夠快追唔到你<br />\n<br />\n單車係一個又平又機動既載具,每人都應該要有一部"},{"pid":"74bbdf0e5d4d1ac0a114212b81738fe969a59c2b","tid":1630701,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dcf1af84221a64e41869978f0b9f180e0faf460b","tid":1630701,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:25:22.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"0caffc5e038cc255936d6b874a157a23a374f669","tid":1630701,"uid":200714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"你on9?"},{"pid":"22ca51e7c32b24d7578b17f603920329fd9be1d4","tid":1630701,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:27:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【政府製造經濟危機】以最和理非既方式 擊敗港共<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630641</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cfaeaf4a57ac03722d500f2bb0ceafa70971e8f","tid":1630701,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:28:37.000Z","msg":"我寧願學parkour"},{"pid":"a1897f51cffcf871d9262f8034391d125338ff15","tid":1630701,"uid":73971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"練好自己部11號車就真"},{"pid":"2c464f5b1477e4ad7fd6c450965e72896fb6a4ed","tid":1630701,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:43:18.000Z","msg":"大陸個種電瓶車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69d76d3fc6ecb2fde7443dd05dafa06a833c66e","tid":1630701,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:43:28.000Z","msg":"變台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d538e02